hadiths[114]{hadithnumber,text}:
2109,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se behtreen shakhs wo hai jisney Quran seekha aur (doosron ko) sikhaya.'' Bukhari ."
2110,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye jabkey ham suffa mein they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se kon pasand karta hai ke wo her roz subh ke waqt wadi Bat'haan ya wadi aqeeq jaey aur koi gunah aur qata rehmi  kiye baghair wahan se badi kohan wali do oontniyaan ley aaye ?'' ham ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham sab usey pasand kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi subh ke waqt masjid kyon nahin aata ke wo Allah Taala ki kitab se do aayaten seekhey ya padhey , to ye uskey liye do oontniyon se behtar hai aur teen ( aayaten ( uskey liye teen ( oontniyon ( se aur chaar , chaar se behtar hain, aur wo jitni ziyada hongi , wo itni hi oontniyon se behtar hongi .'' rawahu Muslim ."
2111,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum mein se koi pasand karta hai ke jab wo apney ghar jaey to wahan teen badi moti tazi hamila oontniyaan paey ?'' ham ne arz kya : ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs apni Namaz mein teen aayaat padhta hai to wo ( teen aayaat ( uskey liye teen moti tazi hamila oontniyon se behtar hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2112,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mahir Quran , itaat guzar moazzaz likhney waley farishton ke sath hoga, aur jo shakhs atak atak kar Quran padhta hai aur wo is par dushwaar hota hai to uskey liye dohra ajr hoga .'' muttafaq aleh."
2113,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sirf do aadmiyon par rashk karna jayez hai, eik wo aadmi jisey Allah ne Quran (ka ilm ( ata kya ho aur wo din raat us ( ki tilawat w amal (ka ehtimam karta ho, aur eik wo aadmi jisey Allah ne maal ata kya ho aur wo din raat is mein se kharch karta ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
2114,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Quran ki tilawat karney wala momin narangi ki tarah hai uski khushbu bhi achi hai aur wo khush zaiqa bhi hai, aur Quran ki tilawat na karney wala momin khajoor ki tarah hai, jiski khushbu nahin lekin uska zaiqa sheereen hai, aur Quran na padhney waley munafiq ki misal تمے ki tarah hai jiski khushbu nahin aur uska zaiqa kadwa hai jabkey Quran padhney wala munafiq naazboo ki tarah hai jiski khushbu achi hai aur zaiqa kadwa hai.'' muttafaq aleh. aur eik riwayat mein hai : '' Quran padhney aur is par amal karney wala momin turanjabin ki misl hai jabkey Quran na padhney wala lekin is par amal karney wala momin khajoor ki tarah hai.''"
2115,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah , is kitab ke zariey kuch logon ko bulandi ata farmata hai aur kuch logon ko pasti ka shikar kar deta hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2116,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Usaid bin Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa wo raat ke waqt Sura Baqra tilawat kar rahey they aur unka ghoda unke paas bandhaa hua tha ke ghoda achcha uchhalney laga , wo khamosh ho gaey to wo (ghodaa) bhi thehar gaya, unhoney phir padha to ghoda phir uchhalney laga wo khamosh ho gaey to wo (ghodaa) bhi thehar gaya. unhoney phir padha to ghoda phir uchhalney laga , wo farigh huye, aur unka beta Yahya us (ghodey) ke qarib hi tha, lihaza unhen andesha hua ke wo usey nuqsan na pahunchaey aur jab unhoney usey door kiya, aur aasman ki taraf sar uthaya to sayeban (saaya) sa dikhai diya jis mein chiraghon ki tarah roshni thi, jab subah hui to unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ibne Huzeer ! padh , ibne Huzeer ! tum padhtey rehtey.'' unhoney arz kiya Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey andesha hua ke (agar main padhta rehta to) wo Yahya ko raund daalta, kyonkey wo uskey qarib tha, lihaza main uski taraf mutawajjeh ho gaya, maine apna sar aasman ki taraf uthaya to (ooper) sayeban (saye) ki tarah koi chiz thi aur is mein chiraghon jaisi koi chiz thi, main bahar nikla yahan tak ke maine us (roshni) ko na dekha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum jantey ho wo kya tha?'' unhoney arz kiya, nahin, farmaya : ''wo farishtey they jo tumhari aawaz ke qarib aagey they, agar tum padhtey rehtey to wo wahin rehtey aur log unhen dekh letey aur wo un se makhfi (chhipey) na rehtey.'' muttafaq aleh. aur ye alfaz hadees Bukhari ke hain, aur Sahih Muslim mein hai : ''main bahar nikla'' seegha mutakallim ke badal lafz : ''wo fiza mein buland ho gaey'' istimal hua hai."
2117,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain eik aadmi Sura kahaf padh raha tha, aur uskey eik janib eik ghoda do mazbut rassiyon se bandhaa hua tha, isliye badal ke tukdey ne us (aadmi) ko dhanp liya aur wo uskey qarib se qarib tar honey laga, jabkey uska ghoda bidakney laga , jab subah hui to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se uska tazkira kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo sakeenat thi jo Quran ki wajeh se nazil hui thi.'' muttafaq aleh."
2118,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed bin Muallaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main masjid mein Namaz padh raha tha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bulaya , maine aap ki aawaz par labbaik kahi, phir main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! main Namaz padh raha tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya Allah ne nahin farmaya ! jab Allah aur uska Rasool tumhen bulaeyn to tum unki itaat karo.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main , is se pehley ke tum masjid se bahar niklo , tumhen Quran ki azeem sura na sikhaun?'' aapney mujhey haath se pakad liya , jab ham ne masjid se bahar nikalney ka irada kiya to maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya tha ke main tumhen Quran ki azeem tar sura sikhaunga , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(الحمد للہ رب العالمین) ''Sura faatih '' wo sabaa-masani aur Qurane-Azeem hai jo mujhey diya gaya hai.''  Bukhari."
2119,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney gharon ko qabristaan na banaao, kyonkey jis ghar mein Sura Baqra ki tilawat ki jaey wahan se shetan bhag jata hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2120,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna ''Quran padha karo, kyonkey wo roze-qiyamat apney padhney walon ke liye sifarishi bin kar aaeyga, Sura Baqra aur Sura Aale-Imran do chamakti hui roshan Suraton ko padho, kyonkey wo qiyamat ke din is haal mein ayengi goya ke wo do badal hain ya do sayebaan hain ya parindon ke ghol hain jo safein baandhey huey apney padhney walon ke haq mein behes w mubaahasa karengey, Sura Baqra padha karo, kyonkey usey hasil kar lena baaise barkat aur isey tarak kar dena baaise hasrat hai, aur jadugar isey hasil nahin kar saktey.'' rawahu Muslim."
2121,"Hazrat Nawaas bin Samaan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Quran aur is par amal karney walon ko roze-qiyamat laya jaeyga, Sura Baqra aur Sura Aale-Imran is (Quran ki soorton) ke aagey hongi goya wo siyah badal hain ya do sayebaan hain unke darmiyan roshni hai, ya wo parindon ke do ghol hain jo safein baandhey huey apney padhney walon ki taraf se jhagda karen gi.'' rawahu Muslim."
2122,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''abu-Munzir! kya tum jantey ho ke tumhen Quran karim ki kon si sab se azeem aayat yad hai? ''maine arz kya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phir farmaya : ''abu-Munzir! kya tum jantey ho ke tumhen Quran karim ki kon si sab se azeem aayat yad hai? ''maine arz kya : (Allahu la Ilaah illa huwal hayyul-qayyum) Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey seeney par haath maara aur farmaya : ''abu-Munzir ! tumhen ilm Mubarak ho.'' ( rawahu muslim) ."
2123,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey sadqa fitr ki hifazat karney par maamoor farmaya , pas eik shakhs merey paas aaya aur ghalley se lappein bharney laga, maine usey pakad liya aur kaha : main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas lekar jaaun ga , usney kaha : main mohtaj hun, merey bachey hain aur main bahut zarurat mand hun, raawi bayan kartey hain, maine usey chhod diya, subh hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Abu-Hurera ! guzishta raat terey qaidi ne kya kya ?'' maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! usney sakht zarurat aur bachon ki shikayat ki to mujhey is par rehem aa gaya aur maine usey chhod diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' usney tumharey sath ghalat bayaani ki aur wo phir aaeyga .'' maine jaan liya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ke mutabiq wo phir aaeyga lihaza mein uski taak mein beth gaya, wo aaya aur ghalla bharney laga to maine usey pakad liya , aur maine kaha : main tumhen zarur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh karunga . usney kaha : main zarurat mand aur ayaal daar hun, main phir nahin aaunga. maine is par taras khatey huey usey chhod diya, subh hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : ''abu-Huraira ! tumharey qaidi ka kya hua ?'' maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! usney sakht zarurat aur bachon ki shikayat ki to maine is par rehem khatey huey usey chhod diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' usney to tum se ghalat bayaani ki aur wo phir aaeyga.'' maine jaan liya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ke mutabiq wo zarur aaeyga . main uski taak mein beth gaya, wo aaya aur ghalla bharney laga to maine usey pakad liya aur kaha : main tumhen zarur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh karunga aur ye teesri aur aakhiri martaba hai, tum kehtey ho mein phir nahin aaunga lekin phir aa jatey ho, usney kaha mujhey chhod do , main tumhen chand kalmaat sikhaaunga jinkey zariey Allah tumhen faeyda pahunchaeyga. jab tum soney ke liye apney bistar par aao to mukammal aayatal-kursi padho, is tarah Allah ki taraf se tum par eik muhafiz muqarrar ho jaeyga aur shetan tumharey qarib nahin aaeyga yahan tak ke subh ho jaeygi, maine usey chhod diya, subh hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' tumharey qaidi ne kya kya?'' maine arz kya, usney kaha ke wo mujhey chand kalmaat sikhaeyga jinkey zariey Allah mujhey faeyda pahunchaeyga , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' usney tum se sach kaha halanke wo jhoota hai, kya tum jantey ho ke tum teen roz se kis ke sath baaten kartey rahey ho ?'' maine arz kya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo shetan tha.'' Bukhari."
2124,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, us doran ke Jibrael (Alaihissalam) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas bethey huey they ke unhoney apney sar ke ooper se zor daar aawaz suni to unhoney apna sar uthaya aur farmaya : ''ye aasman se pehli martaba eik darwaza khula aur us se eik farishta nazil hua hai, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : ye jo farishta zamin ki taraf nazil hua hai, us se pehley kabhi nazil nahin hua hai, usney salam arz kya, to kaha : aap ko do nooron ki khushkhabri ho, wo aap hi ko ata kiye gaey hain, aap se pehley kisi Nabi ko nahin diye gaey, Sura Fatiha aur Sura Baqra ki aakhiri ( teen ( aayaat , aap (aur aap ke muttabein) un dono mein se jo harf ( dua ( padhengey wo aap ko ata kar diya jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2125,"Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Sura Baqra ki aakhiri do aayaten aisi hain ke jo shakhs raat ke waqt unhen padh ley to wo uskey liye kafi ho jati hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
2126,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Sura kahaf ki ibtidaai (shuruati) das aayaat yad kar ley to usey ( fitna ( dajjaal se bacha liya jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2127,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum mein se koi raat mein tihai Quran padhney se aajiz hai? '' Sahaba ne arz kya, tihai Quran kaisey padha ja sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Sura ikhlas tihai Quran ke barabar hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2128,Hazrat Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. Bukhari .
2129,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko kisi lashkar ka ameer bana kar bheja, wo apney sathiyon ko Namaz padhata to qirat ke aakhir mein Sura ikhlas padhta, jab wo wapis aaye to unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska tazkira kya to aapney farmaya : '' us se poochho ke wo aisey kyon karta tha ?'' unhoney us se puchha to usney kaha : kyonkey wo rahmaan ki sift hai, aur main usey padhna pasand karta hun, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey bata do ke Allah usey pasand farmata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2130,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! main Sura ikhlas se mohabbat karta hun, aapney farmaya : '' be-shak tumhari is se mohabbat hi tumhen jannat mein ley jaeygi.'' Tirmizi . aur Imam Bukhari ne uska mafhoom bayan kya hai. Bukhari w Tirmizi ."
2131,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumhen malum nahin ke aaj raat aisi aayaat nazil huin ke un jaisi pehley nahin dekhi gaeen , Sura Falaq aur Sura Naas .'' rawahu Muslim ."
2132,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney bistar par aaram kartey to aap her raat apney dono haath ikhattey kartey, phir Sura ikhlas, Sura Falaq aur Sura Naas padh kar haathon par phunk maartay , phir jahan tak mumkin hota unhen apney jism par phertey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney sar, chehrey aur apney jism ke agley hissey par haath phertey aur aap teen martaba aisa kartey. muttafaq aleh. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Meraj se mutalliq ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees , ham insha Allah Taala ( baab Mairaj ( mein zikr karengey."
2133,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen chizen roze-qiyamat arsh ke nichey hongi , Quran bandon ki taraf se jhagda kerega, uska zahir bhi hai aur baatin bhi, aur amanat bhi, jabkey rehem aawaz dega , sun lo ! jisney mujhey milaya, Allah usey milaaey aur jisney mujhey qata kya Allah usey qata karey.'' Imam Baghwi (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey Sharahus-sunnah mein riwayat kya hai."
2134,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamil w aamile-Quran se kaha jaeyga : padhta ja aur chadhta ja , aur wesay tarteel se padh jaisey to duniya mein tarteel ke sath padha karta tha, aur to jahan aakhiri aayat padhega wahin teri manzil hogi.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
2135,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke pet ( dil ( mein Quran ka kuch hissey na ho wo be-abad ghar ki tarah hai.'' Tirmizi, Darmi aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees sahih hai."
2136,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' rab tabarak w taala farmata hai : Quran ne jis shakhs ko merey zikr aur mujh se sawal karney se mashghool rakha ho main usey us se behtar ata karta hun jo sawal karney walon ko diya jata hai, aur Allah ke kalam ko deegar kalaamon par aisey hi bartari hasil hai jaisey Allah ko apni makhluq par bartari hasil hai.'' ( Tirmizi, Darmi , Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan), aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2137,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Quran karim ka eik harf padhta hai to usey uskey badley main eik neki milti hai, aur neki das guna badh jati hai, main nahin kehta ke) Alif-Lam-Mim (eik harf hai, balke alif eik harf hai, Lam eik harf hai, Mim eik harf hai.'' Tirmizi, Darmi aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. sanad ke lihaz se gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi ."
2138,"Hazrat Haris aa'war (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main masjid se guzra to log baaton mein mashghool they, main Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya aur unhen bataya to unhoney farmaya : kya unhoney aisey kya hai? maine kaha : ji haan, unhoney farmaya : sun lo! be-shak maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''sun lo! an-qareeb fitney paida hongey.'' maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! un se bachney ka kya tariqa hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki kitab, is mein sabiqa qomon ke ahwaal aur mustaqbil ke akhbaar aur tumharey masayel ka hal hai, wo faisla kun hai, be faeyda nahin, jisney az-raah takabbur usey tarak kar diya, Allah ne usey halak kar dala, jisney uskey ilawa kisi aur chiz se hidayat talash karney ki koshish ki to Allah ne usey gumrah kar diya, wo Allah ki mazbut rassi (yani wasila) hai, wo zikr Hakim aur siraate-mustaqeem hai, iski wajeh se khaahishein tedhi hoti hain na zabanen ikhtilaat w iltibas ka shikar hoti hain aur na ulama is se sair hotey hain, kasrate-takraar se wo purani hoti hai aur na hi iskey Ajaaib khatam hotey hain, wo aisi kitab hai ke jisey sun kar jin be-saakhta pukar uthey ke ''ham ne ajab Quran suna hai jo rushd w bhalai ki taraf raahnumai karti hai lihaza ham is par eman ley aaye.'' jisney iskey hawaley se kaha, usney sach kaha, jisney iskey mutabiq amal kya wo ajr pa gaya, jisney iskey mutabiq faisla kya usney adl kya aur jisney iski taraf bulaya wo siraate-mustaqeem ki taraf hidayat pa gaya.'' Tirmizi, Darmi. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : is hadees ki sanad majhool hai aur Haris par kalam kya gaya hai."
2139,"Hazrat Muaz Johni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Quran padha aur uskey mutabiq amal kya to roze-qiyamat uskey waliden ko eik taaj pehnaya jaeyga jiski roshni tumharey duniya ke gharon mein chamakney waley Suraj ki roshni se ziyada achi hogi, tumhara us shakhs ke barey mein kya khayal hai jisney uskey mutabiq amal kya ho! '' ."
2140,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''agar Quran ko chamdey mein rakh kar aag mein dal diya jaey to wo jalega nahin.'' rawahu Darmi."
2141,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney Quran padha , usey yad kya aur uskey halal ko halal aur uskey haram ko haram jana to Allah usey jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga aur uskey ehle khana ke un das afrad ke barey mein uski sifarish qubul farmaeyga jin par jahannam wajib ho chuki thi.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, Darmi . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur Hafs bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) raawi qawi nahin, wo hadees mein zaeef samjha jata hai."
2142,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''tum Namaz mein kaisey qirat kartey ho ?'' unhoney Sura Fatiha padhi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! is jaisi sura Torah w Injeel mein utri hai na Zabur w Quran (yani baqi Quran ( mein, wo saba-masani aur Quran azeem hai jo mujhey diya gaya hai.'' Tirmizi aur Imam Darmi ne ( ماانزلت (ke alfaz se hadees bayan ki hai aur unhoney Ubai bin Kab ka zikr nahin kya, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
2143,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Quran seekho aur usey padho , kyonkey Quran seekhney wala, usey padhney aur uska ehtimam karney wala kastoori se bhari hui thailii ki manind hai jiski khushbu her jagah phel jati hai, aur jisney usey seekha lekin soyaa raha halanke wo Hafiz hai to wo kastoori ki band thailii ki tarah hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
2144,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Sura momin ki pehli aayaat ( الیہ المصیر ( tak aur aayatal-kursi subh ke waqt padhta hai to wo unke sabab Sham tak mehfooz rahega. aur jo shakhs Sham ke waqt unhen padheyga to wo unki wajeh se subh honey tak mehfooz rahega.'' Tirmizi. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
2145,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah ne zamin w aasman ki takhleeq se do hazar saal pehley eik kitab likhi, us se do aayaten utaar kar Sura Baqra ko mukammal kya gaya, aur jis ghar mein unhen teen raat padha jaey to shetan us ( ghar (ke qarib nahin aata.'' Tirmizi, Darmi . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi."
2146,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Sura kahaf ki pehli teen aayaten padhta hai wo fitna dajjaal se mehfooz rahega.'' Tirmizi . aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2147,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her chiz ka dil hota hai aur Quran ka dil Sura Yasin hai, jo shakhs eik martaba Sura Yasin padhta hai to uski qirat ki wajeh se Allah Taala uskey liye das martaba Quran padhney ka sawab likh deta hai.'' Tirmizi, Darmi. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
2148,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ne zamin w aasman ki takhleeq se hazar baras pehley Sura Ta-ha aur Sura Yasin ki tilawat farmaai, jab farishton ne Quran suna to unhoney kaha : is ummat ke liye khushkhabri ho jis par ye utara jaeyga, un Mubarak dilon ke liye khushkhabri ho jo usey yad karengey, aur usey padhney wali zaban ke liye khushkhabri ho.''"
2149,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs raat ke waqt sura Ha-meem Dukhan ki tilawat karta hai to sattar hazar farishtey uskey liye maghfirat talab kartey hain.'' Tirmizi . aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, umr bin abi khasam raawi ko zaeef qarar diya gaya hai, aur Muhammad yani Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : wo munkire-hadees hai."
2150,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Juma ki raat ko Sura Dukhan ki tilawat karta hai to usey bakhsh diya jata hai.'' Tirmizi. aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, neez Hisham abu-Miqdam raawi ko zaeef qarar diya gaya hai."
2151,"Hazrat Irbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) soney se pehley Musabbihaat (Sura Isra, Sura al-Hadeed, al-Hashr, Juma, Taghabun aur Aala) ki tilawat kya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''un main eik aayat hai jo ke hazar aayaat se behtar hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
2152,"Hazrat Imam Darmi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Khalid bin Maadaan se usey mursal riwayat kya hai, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Darmi ."
2153,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Quran mein tees aayaat ki eik sura hai usney eik aadmi ke barey mein sifarish ki yahan tak ke usey bakhsh diya gaya aur wo Sura Mulk hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
2154,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke eik sahabi ne kisi qabr ki jagah par apna khema nasab kya jabkey unhen pata nahin tha wo qabr hai, us main eik insan Sura Mulk padh raha tha yahan tak ke usney usey mukammal kya, pas wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap ko uskey mutalliq bataya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye mania'' aur ''munjiya'' hai usey Allah ke azab se bachaeygi.'' Tirmizi aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
2155,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Sura Sajda aur Sura Mulk padhey baghair nahin sotey they. Ahmed, Tirmizi, Darmi aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees sahih hai. Sharahus-sunnah mein bhi isi tarah hai. jabkey masaabeh mein hai ke ye gharib hai."
2156,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Sura zilzal nisf Quran ke barabar hai, Sura Ikhlas tihai Quran ke baraabar hai aur Sura Kafirun chothai Quran ke barabar hai.''"
2157,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh ke waqt teen martaba اعوذ باللہ السمیع العلیم من الشیطان الرجیم aur Sura al-Hashr ki aakhiri teen aayaat padhta hai to Allah uskey ley sattar hazar farishtey muqarrar farma deta hai, jo Sham tak uskey liye duaaey rehmat kartey rehtey hain, aur agar wo usi roz faut ho jaey to wo shahadat ki maut martaa hai, aur jo shakhs Sham ke waqt unhen padhta hai to usey bhi yehi manzilat w fazilat hasil ho jati hai.'' Tirmizi, Darmi aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai."
2158,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs her roz do so martaba Sura ikhlas padhta hai to qarz ke siwa uskey pachas saal ke gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.'' Tirmizi, Darmi aur unki riwayat mein pachas martaba ka zikr hai, aur unhoney الا ان یکون علیہ دین ke alfaz zikr nahin kiye. ."
2159,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain : ''jo shakhs apney bistar par soney ka irada karey aur apney daain pehlu par let kar so martaba Sura ikhlas padh kar so jaey to roze-qiyamat rab usey farmaeyga : merey bandey! apni daain janib se jannat mein dakhil ho jaao .'' Tirmizi aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
2160,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko Sura ikhlas padhtey huey suna to farmaya : ''wajib ho gaee.'' maine arz kya : kya wajib ho gaee? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat.'' rawahu Malik w Tirmizi w Nasai.
2161,"Hazrat Farwa bin Nofal (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! mujhey koi aisi chiz sikhaein ke jab main bistar par letun to usey padh liya karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Sura Kafirun padha karo kyonkey wo shirk se bara-at (aur tohid ka aelan) hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Darmi."
2162,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Johfa aur Abwa ke darmiyan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath safar kar raha tha ke achcha aandhi aur shadeed tariki ham par chha gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sura Falaq aur Sura Naas ke zariey panah talab karney lagey , aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaney lagey : ''Aqba! un dono ( Suraton (ke zariey panah talab karo, kisi panah talab karney waley ne un dono jaisi panah nahin pai.''"
2163,"Hazrat Abdullah bin khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham barsaat main eik shadeed taareek raat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki talash mein nikley to ham ne aap ko pa liya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kaho .'' maine arz kya, main kya kahun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum subh w Sham teen martaba Sura ikhlas aur Sura Falaq aur Sura Naas padha karo, wo tumhen her chiz ke liye kafi ho jaeyngi.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
2164,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya main Sura Hud padhun ya Sura Yusuf ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Allah ke yahan Sura Falaq se baleegh tar koi chiz nahin padh sakogey.'' rawahu Ahmed w Nasai w Darmi ."
2165,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Quran ke maana bayan karo aur uskey '' gharaaib'' ki ittiba karo, uskey ''gharaaib '' uskey faraaiz w hudood hain.''"
2166,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' dorane-namaz qirat Quran , Namaz ke ilawa qirat Quran se afzal hai, aur Namaz ke ilawa qirate-Quran, tasbih w takbir se afzal hai, aur tasbih (Subhanallah kehna) sadqa se afzal hai, sadqa roza se afzal hai jabkey roza jahannam se dhaal hai.''"
2167,"Hazrat Usman bin Abdullah bin Aus Saqafi apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi ka zabani Quran padhna hazar darjey rakhta hai, jabkey uska Quran karim se dekh kar padhna zabani padhney se do hazar darjey rakhta hai.''"
2168,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye dil zang aalud ho jatey hain jis tarah loha pani lagney se zang aalud ho jata hai.'' arz kya gaya : Allah ke Rasool ! unki chamak kis tarah aati hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' maut ko kasrat se yad karna aur Quran ki tilawat karna.'' Behaqi ne chaaron ahadis ko Shobil-emaan mein zikr kya hai."
2169,"Hazrat Efa bin Abdul-kalaai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! Quran mein sab se azeem sura kon si hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Sura Ikhlas.'' unhoney arz kya : to phir Quran mein sab se azeem aayat kon si hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aayatal-kursi.'' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Nabi ! aap kon si aayat pasand farmatey hain ke wo aap ko aur aap ki ummat ko mil jaey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Sura Baqra ka aakhiri hissey kyonkey wo Allah Taala ke arsh ke nichey uski rehmat ke khazanon mein se hai jo usney is ummat ko ata farmaai hai, aur wo duniya w aakhirat ki tamam bhalaiyon par mushtamil hai.'' ."
2170,"Hazrat Abdul-Malik bin Umer mursal riwayat bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Sura Fatiha mein her bimari se shifa hai.''"
2171,"Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jo shakhs raat ke kisi hisse mein Sura Aale-Imran ka aakhiri hissey padhta hai, uskey liye raat ke qiyam ka sawab likh diya jata hai."
2172,"Hazrat Mak-hool bayan kartey hain, jo shakhs Juma ke roz Sura Aale-Imran padhta hai to raat tak farishtey uskey liye rehmat ki duayen kartey rehtey hain. rawahu Darmi ."
2173,"Hazrat Juber bin Nafair (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah ne Sura Baqra ka ikhtitaam do aayaton se farmaya hai, wo mujhey arsh ke nichey us khazaney se ata ki gaee hain, pas unhen seekho aur unhen apni khawatin ko sikhaao kyonkey wo baais rehmat, baais taqarrub aur dua hain.'' usey Darmi ne mursal riwayat kya hai."
2174,Hazrat Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Juma ke roz Sura Hud padha karo.''
2175,Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Juma ke roz Sura Kahaf padhta hai to uskey liye do jumon ki darmiyani muddat ke liye Noor chamakta rehta hai.'' rawahu al-Behaqi .
2176,"Hazrat Khalid bin Maadaan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, munjiya (azabe-qabr aur hashr se bachaney wali surat) jo ke Sura Sajda hai, padha karo, kyonkey mujhey khabar mili hai ke eik aadmi sirf usey hi padha karta tha jabkey wo bahut gunah gaar tha, isliye is (surat) ne is par apney par bicha diye aur arz kiya, rab ji ! isey bakhsh do, kyonkey wo mujhey kasrat se padha karta tha, rab taala ne uskey mutalliq uski sifarish qubul farma li, aur farmaya : ''iski her ghalati ke badley uskey liye neki likh do aur iska darja buland kar do.'' aur unhon (Khalid bin Maadaan) ne ye bhi kaha : ''wo apney padhney waley ke mutalliq qabr mein jhagda karegi aur kahegi : aey Allah ! agar main teri kitab mein se hun to phir iskey mutalliq meri sifarish qubul farma , aur agar main teri kitab mein se nahin hun to phir mujhey is se khatam farma dey, aur wo parindey ki tarah hogi aur is par apney par phela dey gi, wo uski sifarish karegi aur usey azabe-qabr se bacha leygi.'' aur unhon (Khalid bin Maadaan) ne Sura Mulk ke mutalliq bhi isi tarah bayan kiya hai, aur wo un dono Suraton ko padhey baghair nahin soyaa kartey they, aur Taaus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain un dono Suraton ko Quran ki her sura par saath (60) nekiyon se fazilat di gaee hai."
2177,"Hazrat Ata bin Abi Ribah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mujhey khabar pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs din ke pehley hissey mein Sura Yasin padhta hai to uski tamam zarooriyaat puri kar di jati hain.'' Imam Darmi ne isey mursal riwayat kiya hai."
2178,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ki raza ki khatir Sura Yasin padhta hai to uskey sabiqa gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain, isey apney qaribul-marg (maut ke qareeb) afrad ke paas padha karo.''"
2179,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : her chiz ki eik choti hoti hai aur Quran ki choti Sura Baqra hai, aur her chiz ka eik maghz (dimagh) hota hai aur Quran ka maghz (dimagh) mufassal (tafseeli) suraten (Sura al Hujuraat se Naas tak) hain.'' rawahu Darmi."
2180,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' her chiz ka Husn aur jamaal hota hai jabkey Quran ka Husn aur jamaal Sura Rehman hai.''"
2181,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs her raat Sura waqia padhta hai to wo kabhi faaqey ka shikar nahin hoga. aur ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) apni betiyon ko hukm diya kartey they ke wo her raat isey padha karen. Imam Behaqi ne in dono ko Shobul-emaan mein riwayat kiya hai."
2182,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is surat, Sura Aa'la ko pasand kartey they."
2183,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey padhaein, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''الرٰٓ wali Suraton (Yunus, hood, yousuf, Ibrahim, Al Hijr) mein se teen suraten padho.'' usney arz kiya : main umr raseeda (budha) ho gaya hun, mera dil sakht ho gaya hai aur meri zaban moti ho gaee hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Haa-Meem wali Suraton ( المومن , الفصلت , الشوری , الزخرف , Dukhan , الجاشیہ , الاحقاف ( mein se teen suraten padho.'' usney phir wohi arz kiya, us aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey koi Jaame sura padhaein, to phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey Sura Zilzaal puri padhaai to us aadmi ne arz kiya, us zaat ki qism ! jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja , main is par kabhi bhi izafa na karunga, phir wo aadmi wapis chala gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do martaba farmaya : ''wo aadmi falah pa gaya.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
2184,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum mein se koi her roz hazar aayat padhney ki taqat nahin rakhta?'' unhoney arz kiya, her roz hazar aayat kon padh sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum mein se koi Sura Takasur nahin padh sakta?''"
2185,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mursal riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs das martaba Sura Ikhlas padhta hai to uskey badle mein uskey liye jannat main eik mehal bana diya jata hai, jo shakhs bees martaba padhta hai to uskey liye jannat mein do mehal bana diye jatey hain aur jo shakhs tees martaba padhta hai to uskey liye uskey badle mein jannat mein teen mehal bana diye jatey hain.'' umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! tab to ham apney mehal ziyada kar lengey, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah is se bhi ziyada kashaaish (kushadgi wala) aur faraakhi wala hai.'' rawahu Darmi."
2186,"Hazrat Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) se mursal riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs raat mein sau aayaat tilawat karta hai to us raat Quran us se jhagda nahin karta, jo shakhs raat mein do sau aayaat padhta hai to uskey liye raat bhar ka qiyam likh diya jata hai, aur jo shakhs raat mein paanch sau se hazar aayaat tilawat karta hai to subah ke waqt uskey liye dheron ajr hoga.'' unhoney arz kiya, dheron se kya murad hai? farmaya : ''baara hazar.''"
2187,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Quran ki khabar geeri kartey raho , us zaat ki qism jiskey haathon mein meri jaan hai ! wo (Quran seenon sey) nikal janey mein , us oont ke nikal janey se bhi ziyada tez hai jiski rassi khul chuki ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
2188,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi ke liye ye kehna bahut hi bura hai ke main falan aayat bhool gaya hun, balke (yun kahiye) mujhey bhula di gaee hai, Quran yad kartey raha karo kyonkey wo aadmiyon ke seenon se nikal janey mein khuley huey oonton se bhi ziyada tez hai.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur Imam Muslim ne : (بعقلھا) ke alfaz ka izafa kiya hai. muttafaq aleh."
2189,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haafize-Quran, bandhey huey oonton ke Malik ki tarah hai, agar wo uska khayal rakhega to usey rokey rakhega aur agar usey chhod dega to wo chaley jaeyngey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2190,"Hazrat Jundub bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Quran us waqt tak padho jab tak tumharey dil is par mutawajjeh hon, aur jab tumharey khayalat muntashir ho (bhtak) jaeyn to phir isey padhna chhod do.'' muttafaq aleh."
2191,"Hazrat Qatada bayan kartey hain, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat ke barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : wo mad ke sath thi, phir unhoney (بسم اللہ الرحمن الرحیم) padhi  aur (بسم اللہ) aur (الرحمن) aur (الرحیم) ko mad ke sath padha (yani lamba karkey padha). Bukhari."
2192,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne itni tawajjoh se kisi chiz ko nahin suna jitna usney Nabi ko tarannum ke sath Quran padhtey huey tawajjoh se suna.'' muttafaq aleh."
2193,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne itni tawajjoh se kisi chiz ko nahin suna jitna usney apney Nabi ko achchhi aur buland aawaz ke sath Quran padhtey huey suna.'' muttafaq aleh."
2194,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs achchhi aawaz se Quran nahin padhta wo ham mein se nahin.'' Bukhari."
2195,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par they ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''mujhey Quran sunaao.'' maine arz kiya, main aap ko Quran sunaun, jabkey wo aap par nazil kiya gaya hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main apney ilawa kisi aur se isey sunna chahta hun.'' maine Sura Nisa tilawat ki yahan tak ke jab main is aayat (فَكَيْفَ اِذَا جِئْنَا مِنْ كُلِّ اُمَّةٍۢ بِشَهِيْدٍ وَّجِئْنَا بِكَ عَلٰي هٰٓؤُلَاء شَهِيْدًا) par pahuncha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ab bas karo.'' maine aap ki taraf dekha to aap ki aankhon mein aansu aa gaey. muttafaq aleh."
2196,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''Allah ne mujhey hukm farmaya hai ke main tumhen Quran sunaaun.'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah ne mera naam liya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' unhoney arz kiya, mera Rabbul-Aalameen ke yahan zikr kiya gaya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' (ye sun kar) unki aakhon mein (khushi ke) aansu bahney lagey. aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''Allah ne mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tumhen Sura Bayyena sunaaun.'' unhoney arz kiya, mera naam lekar (aap ko bataya hai)? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' isliye wo roney lagey. muttafaq aleh."
2197,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Quran lekar dushman ki sar zamin (daarul-harab) ki taraf safar karney se mana farmaya. Bukhari, Muslim aur Muslim ki eik riwayat mein hai : ''Quran lekar safar na karo, kyonkey agar dushman (yani kafir ( usey pa ley to mujhey (us ki be-hurmati ka ( andesha hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2198,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main muhajrin ki eik kamzor jamaat ke sath betha hua tha, aur un mein se baaz (aam libas ki wajeh sey) barahna (nanga) honey ki wajeh se eik doosrey ke peechhey chupey huey they aur qaari hamein Quran suna raha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur aa kar khadey ho gaey, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho gaey to qaari khamosh ho gaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salam kiya aur phir farmaya : ''tum kya kar rahey they?'' ham ne arz kiya ham ba-ghaur Quran karim sun rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney meri ummat mein aisey afrad bana diye jinkey paas theherney ka mujhey hukm diya gaya hai.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey wast (beech) mein beth gaey taake aap ham sab ko barabar sharf bakhsh saken, phir aapney apney haath se is tarah ishara farmaya to unhoney halqa bana liya aur wo sab aap ke samney aa gaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''muhajrin ki jamaat fuqaraa ! tumhen qiyamat ke roz mukammal Noor ki khushkhabri ho, tum maal daar logon se nisf (aadha) saal pehley, aur wo paanch sau saal hai, jannat mein jaaogey.''"
2199,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni aawaazon ke zariey Quran ko muzayyan karo (sajaao).'' rawahu Ahmed, Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2200,"Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Quran padhta ho lekin phir wo usey bhool jaey to wo roze-qiyamat haalate-kodh mein Allah se mulaqat kerega.''"
2201,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs teen din se kam muddat mein Quran khatam karta hai to wo Quran fehmi se mehroom rehta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
2202,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''buland aawaz se Quran padhney wala, elaniya sadqa karney waley ki tarah hai, jabkey aahista Quran padhney wala chhupa kar sadqa karney waley ki tarah hai.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
2203,"Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us shakhs ka Quran par eman nahin jo uski haram karda ashiya (chezon) ko halal janta hai.'' Tirmizi. Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : is hadees ki sanaad qawi nahin."
2204,"Hazrat Leis bin Saad , ibne-Abi Muleka sey, wo Yaa'la bin Mumlik se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat ke barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat wazeh aur harf-harf (yani alag alag) thi. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
2205,"Hazrat ibne-Juraij , ibne-Abi Muleka se aur wo Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni qirat thehar-thehar kar kiya kartey they, aap (الحمد للہ رب العالمین) padhtey, phir waqf farmatey phir (الرحمن الرحیم) padhtey phir waqf farmatey they. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : iski sanad muttasil nahin, kyonkey Leis ne ye hadees ibne-abi Muleka an Yaa'laa bin Mumlik ne Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki sanad se riwayat ki hai, aur Leis ki hadees ziyada sahih hai."
2206,"Hazrat Jabir bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye to ham Quran padh rahey they aur ham mein Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) aur ajmi (ghair Arabi) bhi they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''padho, sab theek hai. an-qareeb aisey log aaeyngey jo isey is tarah (mubaalgha ke sath) durust karengey jaisey teer durust kiya jata hai. wo duniya main hi jaza chahen gey aur isey aakhirat tak muakhkhar (der karke) nahin karengey.'' (yani wo talabe-duniya ke liye padhengey) rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Al-Behaqi."
2207,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Quran, Arbi lahje aur Arbi aawaz se padha karo aur ehle ishaq aur yahood aur Nasara ke lajon se bacho, aur merey baad aisey log aaeyngey jo naghmey aur nauhe ki tarah aawaz dohra dohra kar Quran padhengey, aur wo (Quran ka padhna) unke halaq se nichey (dil tak) nahin utreyga . unke aur un logon ke dil , jo unki haalat par farefta hongey, fitne se dochaar hongey.'' (Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) aur Razeen ne isey apni kitab mein riwayat kiya hai. (munkir)."
2208,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''apni aawaazon se Quran ko Husain banaao, kyonkey achchhi aawaz , Quran ke Husn mein izafa karti hai.'' rawahu Darmi."
2209,"Hazrat Taaus (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya, kon log achchhi aawaz aur achchhi qirat se Quran padhtey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey tum Quran padhtey suno aur is par dar Ilahi zahir ho.'' Taaus bayan kartey hain, Talaq (Raziallahu anhu) isi tarah they."
2210,"Hazrat Ubeda Mulaiki (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ehale Quran ! Quran ke mamley mein susti aur taghaaful (ghaflat) na barto, jaisey iski tilawat ka haq hai wesay subah aur Sham iski tilawat karo, is (ki ta'leemaat) ko aam karo, iskey ilawa dusri chizon se be-niyaz ho jaao, is par taddabur karo taake tum falah pa jaao, duniya mein iska sawab hasil karney ki koshish na karo kyonkey (aakhirat mein) iska sawab (bahut ziyada) hai.''"
2211,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Hisham bin Hakim bin Juzaam (Raziallahu anhu) ko Sura Furqan us andaz se hat kar padhtey huey suna jis andaz se main usey padhta tha aur jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey sikhaya tha, qarib tha ke main fauran us se chhed-chhaad aur inkar karta, lekin maine usey mohlat di yahan tak ke wo (qirat sey) farigh ho gaya, phir maine uski gardan mein uski chadar dali aur usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein la kar arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine isey us andaz se hat kar Sura furqan padhtey huey suna hai jis andaz se aapney usey mujhey padhaya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey chhod do, (aur usey farmaya) padho.'' usney usi qirat se padha jo maine us se suni thi, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isi tarah nazil ki gaee hai.'' phir mujhey farmaya : ''padho.'' maine padha to farmaya : ''isi tarah nazil ki gaee hai kyonkey Quran saat lahjon mein mujh par utara gaya hai, un mein se jis lehje mein aasani se padh sako padho.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur alfaze hadees Muslim ke hain. muttafaq aleh."
2212,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine eik aadmi ko Quran padhtey huey suna jabkey maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko us se mukhtalif padhtey huey suna tha, main usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaya aur aap ko bataya to maine aap ke chehre Mubarak par nagawari ke asraat dekhay, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum dono theek ho, baham (aapas mein) ikhtilaf na karo, kyonkey jo log tum se pehley they, unhoney ikhtilaf kiya to wo halak ho gaey.'' Bukhari."
2213,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main masjid mein tha ke eik aadmi aaya aur Namaz padhney laga , usney us andaz se qirat ki ke maine us qirat ko ghair maroof aur ajnabi sa mehsus kiya, phir doosra aadmi aaya to usney apney sathi ki qirat ke ilawa eik doosrey andaz mein qirat ki, jab ham ne Namaz padh li to ham sab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to maine arz kiya, is shakhs ne qirat ki to maine uska inkar kiya, phir doosra shakhs aaya to usney apney sathi ki qirat ke ilawa doosrey andaz mein qirat ki, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un dono ko (padhney ka ( hukm farmaya to un dono ne qirat ki to aapney unki haalat (qirat) ko saraahaa to merey dil mein takzeeb (jhutlaane) ka aisa shubha paida ho gaya jo ke merey daure-jahiliyat mein bhi nahin tha, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh par taari kaifiyat dekhi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey seeney par haath maara to main paseeney se shraabor ho gaya aur mujh par aisa khof taari hua ke goya main Allah ko dekh raha hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' Abi ! mujhey pegham bheja gaya ke main eik lahje par Quran padhun, lekin maine us (qaasid) ko Allah Taala ki taraf wapis bheja ke meri ummat par aasani ki jaey, dusri martaba ye pegham aaya ke main isey do lahjon mein padhun, maine phir usey wapis bheja ke meri ummat par aasani ki jaey, teesri martaba ye pegham aaya ke main isey saat lahjon mein padhun, aur aap ke her baar lautane ke badley eik maqbool dua hai lihaza aap dua karen, maine arz kiya, aey Allah ! meri ummat ko bakhsh dey, aey Allah ! meri ummat ko bakhsh dey, aur maine teesri martaba ko us roz ke liye taal kar rakh liya jis roz tamam log yahan tak ke Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) meri taraf raghbat (dilchaspi) aur ruju karengey.'' rawahu Muslim."
2214,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne mujhey eik lahje par padhaya to maine usey wapis bheja mein un se mazeed (lahjon) ki darkhast karta raha aur wo mujhey mazeed (lahje) ata farmatey rahey yahan tak ke saat lahjen mukammal huey.'' ibne-Shahab bayan kartey hain, mujhey ye baat pahunchi ke wo saat lahje Deen ke mamley main eik hi hain, wo halal aur haram mein mukhtalif nahin. muttafaq aleh."
2215,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jibrael (Alaihissalam) se miley farmaya : ''Jibrael ! mujhey eik an-padh ummat ki taraf bhejaa gaya hai, un mein se kuchh boodhi aurten hain, kuchh boodhey aadmi hain, chhotey bachchey aur bachchiyaan hain, aur aisey aadmi bhi hain jinhon ne kabhi koi kitab nahin padhi.'' unhoney farmaya : ''Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! Quran saat lahjon par utara gaya hai. Tirmizi, Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''un mein se her eik (lahja) poora aur kafi hai.'' aur Nasai ki riwayat hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael aur Mekael merey paas aaye to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) merey daain jabkey Mekael merey baain taraf beth gaey, to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : Quran ko eik lahje par padho , Mekael (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : in se ziyada talab karen, yahan tak ke wo saat lahjon par pahunchey, aur her lahja poora aur kafi hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Ahmed, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
2216,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo eik waaiz ke paas se guzrey jo ke Quran padhta , phir kuchh talab karta , is par unhoney (Inna lillah w inna ilaihi raajioon) padha phir kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs Quran padhey to wo Allah se talab karey, kyonkey aisey log bhi aaeyngey jo Quran padhengey aur uskey iwaz logon se sawal karengey.''"
2217,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Quran padhta hai aur uskey zariey logon se maal (khata) hai to wo roze-qiyamat aaeyga to uska chehra haddiyon ka dhaancha hoga is par gosht nahin hoga.''"
2218,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (بسم اللہ الرحمن الرحیم) ke nazil honey ke baad sura ke farq ka pata chalta tha. (ke pehli sura mukammal ho gaee hai) rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2219,"Hazrat Alqama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham teiswin (mulke Shaam) mein they, to ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Sura Yusuf tilawat farmaai to kisi aadmi ne kaha : is tarah to nazil nahin hui, to Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! maine isey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein padha tha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya tha : ''tum ne bahut khub padha.'' is beech mein ke wo shakhs un se baaten kar raha tha to unhoney us se sharab ki boo mehsus ki to unhoney farmaya : kya tum sharab peetey ho aur Quran ki takzeeb kartey (jhutlaate) ho? isliye unhoney is par had qaaim ki . muttafaq aleh. Alqama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham teiswin (mulk Shaam) mein they, to ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Sura Yusuf tilawat farmaai to kisi aadmi ne kaha : is tarah to nazil nahin hui, to Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! maine isey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein padha tha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya tha : ''tum ne bahut khub padha.'' is beech mein ke wo shakhs un se baaten kar raha tha to unhoney us se sharab ki bo mehsus ki to unhoney farmaya : kya tum sharab peetey ho aur Quran ki takzeeb kartey (jhutlaate) ho? isliye unhoney is par had qaaim ki. muttafaq aleh."
2220,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ladaai yamaama ke baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne meri taraf pegham bheja , umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas mojud they. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : umr merey paas aaye to unhoney farmaya : ladaai yamaama mein bahut se qaari Shahid ho gaey, aur mujhey andesha hua ke agar kisi aur ladaai mein qaari Shahid ho gaey to is tarah Quran ka bahut sa hissey jata rahega, aur main samajhta hun ke aap jama Quran ka hukm farmaeyn, lekin maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : aap wo kaam kaisey karengey jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne nahin kiya? to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! ye (jama Quran) behtar hai, umr (Raziallahu anhu) musalsal mujhey kehtey rahey yahan tak ke Allah ne is kaam ke liye mera Sina khol diya aur ab is mein meri wohi raaye hai jo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hai. Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aap aql mand nojawan hain aur aap par kisi qism ka koi ilzam nahin, aur aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wahi likha kartey they, aap Quran ikhatta karen aur usey eik jagah jama karen, Allah ki qism ! agar wo mujhey kisi pahad ko muntaqil karney par maamoor farmatey to wo mujh par is jama Quran ke hukm se ziyada aasan tha, wo (Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) bayan kartey hain. maine kaha : tum wo kaam kaisey kartey ho jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne nahin kiya? to unhon (Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! wo behtar hai, isliye Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) musalsal mujhey kehtey rahey yahan tak ke Allah ne is kaam ke liye mera Sina khol diya jis ke liye usney Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina khol diya tha, maine Quran talash karna shuru kiya aur maine khajoor ki shaakhon, pathar ki silon aur logon ke seenon (Haafizon) se Quran ikhatta kiya yahan tak ke maine Sura Tauba ka aakhiri hissa (لقد جاءکم رسول من انفسکم) aakhir tak sirf Abu Khuzaima Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan paya, wo saheefa (Quran karim ka nuskha) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas raha yahan tak ke Allah ne unhen faut kar diya, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki zindagi mein unke paas raha, aur phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke paas. Bukhari."
2221,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye jabkey wo (Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) Aarminiya aur Aazar-baaijaan se ladaai aur Fateh ke silsiley mein ahle-Sham aur ahle Iraq ko tayyar kar rahey they, Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) un (ahle-Sham aur Iraq) ke ikhtilafe-qirat ki wajeh se pareshan they, Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ameerul-momeneen ! is se pehley ke ye ummat yahood aur Nasara ki tarah Quran karim ke barey mein ikhtilaf ka shikar ho jaey aap iska hal nikaalen, Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf pegham bheja ke wo hamen musahaf (kitab) bhejein, ham iski naqalein tayyar karkey wapis dey dengey , Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne wo nuskha Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bhej diya to unhoney Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) , Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) , Saeed bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abdullah bin Haris bin Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) ko maamoor farmaya to unhoney uski naqalein tayyar kin , aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne teeno quraishiyon se farmaya : jab Quran ki kisi chiz ke barey main tumharey aur Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ke beech koi ikhtilaf ho jaey to usey zabane-Quraish ke mutabiq likhna , kyonkey Quran unki zaban mein utra hai, unhoney aisey hi kiya, yahan tak ke jab unhoney musahaf (kitab) se naqalein tayyar kar leen to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo musahaf (kitab), Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ko wapis kar diya, aur tamam ilaqon mein wo naqal ki hui kitab bhej den. aur hukm jari kar diya ke iskey ilawa kisi ke paas Quran ka jo nuskha hai usey jala diya jaey, ibne-Shahab bayan kartey hain, khaarija bin Zaid bin Sabit ne mujhey bataya ke Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke jab ham ne musahaf (kitab) ki naqal tayyar ki to Sura Ehzaab ki wo aayat , jo main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna karta tha, na mili to ham ne usey talash kiya to ham ne usey Khuzaima bin Sabit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan paya , wo aayat ye thi (من المومنین رجال صدقوا ما عاھدوا اللہ علیہ) isliye ham ne usey musahaf mein uski Sura Ehzaab mein mila diya. Bukhari."
2222,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : tumhen kis chiz ne aamada kiya hai ke tum ne Sura Anfaal ka qasd (irada) (irada) kiya jabkey wo masaani (soorton mein se) hai, aur Sura bara-at (tauba) ka qasd (irada) kiya jabkey wo do sau aayaton wali Suraton mein se hai, aur tum ne un dono Suraton ko milaya aur tum ne unke darmiyan (بسم اللہ الرحمن الرحیم) bhi nahin likhi , aur tum ne usey saat lambi Suraton mein rakh diya, aisa karney par kis chiz ne tumhen ubhaaraa? Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ye soorate-haal thi ke kabhi taweel waqt guzar jata aur aap par koi sura nazil na hoti aur bahut si aayaat wali suraten nazil hotin, aur jab aap par kuchh hissey nazil hota to aap kisi 'kaatibe wahi' ko bulatey aur usey farmatey : ''in aayaat ko , falan sura mein jahan falan falan tazkira hai, shamil kar do.'' Sura Anfaal wo sura hai jo qiyame-Madina ke ibtidaai (shuruati) daur mein nazil hui thi, jabkey Sura bara-at (tauba) nuzool ke lihaz sey, Nuzoole-Quran ke aakhiri daur mein nazil hui, aur ba-lihaaz mazmoon dono eik doosrey ke mushabeh thin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wafat pa gaey aur aapney wazahat na farmaai ke wo (Sura tauba) us (Sura Anfaal) mein se hai, isi liye maine un dono ko mila liya aur (بسم اللہ الرحمن الرحیم) na likhi, aur maine isey saat lambi Suraton mein shamil kiya. rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
